annotationA: Vacuolar protein sorting-associated protein 72 homolog; Part of the Tip60 chromatin-remodeling complex which is involved in DNA repair. Upon induction of DNA double-strand breaks, this complex acetylates phosphorylated H2AV in nucleosomes and exchanges it with unmodified H2AV
annotationB: MRG/MORF4L binding protein; It is involved in the biological process described with: regulation of transcription, DNA-templated; neurogenesis
